Package: eClassic
Title: Efficient Classic & Traditional Factors Toolkit for Quantitative Research in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yishuo",
           family = "Deng",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dengyishuo@163.com")
Description: A fast, lightweight R package for computing classic and traditional quantitative
    factors such as size, value, momentum, profitability, quality, volatility,
    and liquidity. It provides helper functions for quantitative research
    and multi-factor model development.
